This repo represents a WIP graft onto the Firefox mochitest tree of mozilla-central.

To deploy:

1) Clone mozilla-central
2) cd mozilla-central/dom/tests/mochitest
3) Clone this repo as:

git clone <address> webapps

4) cd webapps
5) Run the following command to add the webapps directory to mochitest:

patch -d .. < parentMakefile.patch

6) Finally, from the top of mozilla-central, build Firefox.

If you've already built Firefox and just want to graft this in,

Perform steps 1-5 as above
6) From the top of mozilla-central, cd <OBJ-DIR>/dom/tests
7) make

